---
By: Hui-Neng
Source:
  Page: 93
  Title: The Heart Sutra
  Translator: Red Pine
Title: The Bodhi Tree and the Mirror
---
Shen-hsiu wrote：

    The body is a bodhi tree,
    the mind a spotless mirror.
    keep it always clean
    don't let it gather dust.

Hui-neng replied：

    Bodhi isn't a tree,
    what's spotless isn't a mirror
    actually, there isn't a thing
    where do you get this dust?
